{"tid":1993394,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"可受教主楊丞琳有冇同小豬做過愛？","createTime":"2020-04-28T17:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T18:49:15.000Z","uid":93112,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"22c3a8a56832bc9c4754a57449e7f77b41f52987","tid":1993394,"uid":93112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"羅志祥演唱會強吻楊丞琳，對方反露甜蜜樣。楊丞琳稱身材被羅志祥看光，嬌喊把她娶回家。2010年5月3日，羅志祥在香港紅館舉行《舞法舞天世界巡回演唱會》，可愛教主楊丞琳以性感打扮擔任嘉賓，二人在台上旁若無人打情罵俏。楊丞琳輕咬羅志祥手指，羅志祥乘機捉緊她並偷吻她的臉頰，楊丞琳反而露出甜蜜樣，惹得台下粉絲尖叫。羅志祥和楊丞琳二人因合作《海派甜心》相識，之後一直都有緋聞傳出，然而羅志祥曾堅決否認，稱對方只是好朋友，自己是單身。2012年，在微電影《再一次心跳》首日瀏覽率破300萬慶功會，羅志祥還曾大贊楊丞琳「皮膚很好!」，楊丞琳臉紅回應說：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">「正面背面(身材)都被你看光了，還抱著我腳不放，在古代的話你就要把我娶回家了啦！」</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2g2gAG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2g2gAG.png&h=29ce7d2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y0auF2n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY0auF2n.png&h=cc8796d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G00Ob84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG00Ob84.jpg&h=665634eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKbxDO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKbxDO5.jpg&h=22666a4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a220c4c37eef792d32fc9fe3dca3d27828b67a8","tid":1993394,"uid":94828,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:40:35.000Z","msg":"話冇冇人信"},{"pid":"d23cc8b31db1faacc5c35de6bcc9a01a7826c75d","tid":1993394,"uid":342386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:43:15.000Z","msg":"同小鬼一齊3p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb23272092d38fe2d39c2ec52dacde868d1fca23","tid":1993394,"uid":57776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:47:56.000Z","msg":"點會冇"},{"pid":"e833b2b1f95e444b6df0666a58c2446103dd37cc","tid":1993394,"uid":43809,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:55:15.000Z","msg":"應該係問做過幾多次"},{"pid":"3e488861a32923166ac8eb6d1abf2bddf0161fe2","tid":1993394,"uid":93112,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:55:44.000Z","msg":"李榮浩碌鳩都唔野小，楊識簡男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76db2972e38c747bbfe3ce9b344ac9169629a0b2","tid":1993394,"uid":280853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:57:08.000Z","msg":"有 ，完，咪撚再講啦，好悶。<br />\n問隻雞有無比人屌，多鳩餘。"},{"pid":"257b24f92e21a848bcb7b12114874b81d56042e7","tid":1993394,"uid":6842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e488861a32923166ac8eb6d1abf2bddf0161fe2","tid":1993394,"uid":93112,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:55:44.000Z","msg":"李榮浩碌鳩都唔野小，楊識簡男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:58:59.000Z","msg":"你點知的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce0ba06b77e16624070963a67121f1945fcb1f5","tid":1993394,"uid":172349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T18:00:20.000Z","msg":"楊丞琳重係處女"},{"pid":"0b0fbbb42a8d72dc7e828916023eb19bf3b83925","tid":1993394,"uid":343401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T18:21:44.000Z","msg":"聽講佢都麻麻地小豬？"},{"pid":"227590a9a5003acfe35d9d6520e204799bc1a538","tid":1993394,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ce0ba06b77e16624070963a67121f1945fcb1f5","tid":1993394,"uid":172349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T18:00:20.000Z","msg":"楊丞琳重係處女"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T18:49:15.000Z","msg":"楊臣又咁出名"}]}